Email communication is one of the most widely used forms of digital communication. However, with its growth, the problem of spam emails has also increased significantly. Spam emails are unsolicited messages that may contain advertisements, phishing links, or harmful content.

This project focuses on building an **AI/ML-based Spam Email Classifier** that automatically categorizes emails into *Spam* and *Ham (Not Spam)* using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques.

